{"id":"swarm-cli-autoresearch-oclif-001","title":"Evaluar migración a oclif para CLI framework","description":"Investigar migración gradual a oclif (framework de Heroku/Salesforce) para mejorar la arquitectura del CLI. Evaluar: sistema de plugins nativo, generación automática de docs, autocomplete integrado, testing framework. Crear spike de POC comparando comandos actuales vs estructura oclif.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"research","created_at":"2026-03-11T07:47:00.000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-11T07:47:00.000Z","parent_id":null,"dependencies":[],"labels":["autoresearch","cli-framework","oclif","spike"],"comments":[],"research_source":"memory/autoresearch/2026-03-11-cli-frameworks.md"}
{"id":"swarm-cli-autoresearch-temporal-001","title":"Integrar Temporal para durable execution de agentes","description":"Evaluar Temporal.io como orquestador de workflows para agentes del swarm. Ventajas: durable execution (agentes corren días sin perder estado), OpenAI Agents SDK integration oficial, TypeScript SDK, state recovery automático. Crear POC de un 'run' como Temporal workflow.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"research","created_at":"2026-03-11T07:47:00.000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-11T07:47:00.000Z","parent_id":null,"dependencies":[],"labels":["autoresearch","orchestration","temporal","durable-execution"],"comments":[],"research_source":"memory/autoresearch/2026-03-11-agent-orchestration.md"}
{"id":"swarm-cli-autoresearch-pglite-001","title":"Migrar estado a PGlite (Postgres en WASM)","description":"Reemplazar archivos JSON (.hive/issues.jsonl) por base de datos PGlite embebida. Beneficios: SQL completo, pgvector para embeddings, ~3MB bundle, reactive bindings. Stack propuesto: PGlite (cliente) + ElectricSQL (sync). Crear POC migrando el sistema de issues actual.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"research","created_at":"2026-03-11T07:47:00.000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-11T07:47:00.000Z","parent_id":null,"dependencies":["swarm-cli-electric-sql-001"],"labels":["autoresearch","database","pglite","local-first","wasm"],"comments":[],"research_source":"memory/autoresearch/2026-03-11-local-first-databases.md"}
{"id":"swarm-cli-autoresearch-knowledge-001","title":"Implementar sistema de knowledge two-tier","description":"Diseñar e implementar sistema de conocimiento inspirado en OpenCode Swarm. Dos niveles: Swarm-Level (.swarm/knowledge.jsonl - lecciones proyecto) y Hive-Level (~/.config/swarm-cli/knowledge.jsonl - sabiduría cross-proyecto). Features: auto-promote después de 30 días, confidence/utility scoring, deduplicación, quarantine system. Incluye retrospectivas automáticas post-phase.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"research","created_at":"2026-03-11T07:47:00.000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-11T07:47:00.000Z","parent_id":null,"dependencies":[],"labels":["autoresearch","knowledge","memory","learning","opencode-swarm"],"comments":[],"research_source":"https://www.swarmai.site/docs#persistence"}
{"id":"swarm-cli-resume-capability-001","title":"Implementar resume capability con PLAN.md","description":"Permitir que el swarm pueda resumir ejecución después de interrupciones. El agente 'architect' debe chequear si PLAN.md existe al iniciar y restaurar el estado exacto donde se quedó. Incluye: parseo de plan.md, restauración de contexto de agentes, y continuación del workflow desde el último task completado.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-03-11T07:48:00.000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-11T07:48:00.000Z","parent_id":null,"dependencies":["swarm-cli-7a7cye-mmjozhfhrc7"],"labels":["resume","state","plan.md","reliability"],"comments":[],"reference":"https://www.swarmai.site/docs#architect-workflow-modes"}
