{"id":"swarm-cli-agents-specialized-001","title":"Definir 9 agentes especializados del swarm","description":"Especificar y documentar los 9 agentes especializados del swarm (inspirado en OpenCode Swarm): architect (orquestador), explorer (codebase scanner), sme (domain expert), critic (plan reviewer), coder (implementación), reviewer (code review), test_engineer (tests + adversarial), designer (UI/scaffolding), docs (documentación). Cada agente debe tener: rol definido, triggers de ejecución, modelos recomendados, y permisos específicos.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-03-11T07:48:00.000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-11T07:48:00.000Z","dependencies":[],"labels":["agents","architecture","roles","spec"],"comments":[]}
