{"id":"swarm-cli-quality-gates-001","title":"Implementar 7 Quality Gates para validación de tareas","description":"Diseñar e implementar 7 quality gates obligatorios que cada tarea debe pasar antes de completarse (inspirado en OpenCode Swarm). Gates propuestos: 1) diff + imports (contract analysis), 2) syntax_check, 3) placeholder_scan (TODOs/stubs), 4) build_check, 5) pre_check_batch (lint, secretscan, SAST), 6) reviewer_pass (correctness + security), 7) test_engineer_pass (tests + coverage ≥70%). Si un gate falla, el agente recibe feedback estructurado y reintenta.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-03-11T07:48:00.000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-11T07:48:00.000Z","dependencies":[],"labels":["agents","quality-gates","validation","workflow"],"comments":[]}
